• Documentation and reporting as required;
• Travelling as required.

Job Requirements:
• Minimum of 8 years’ of experience supporting infrastructure servers, cloud environments and networks;
• Strong experience working with technology vendors, including Microsoft, VMware, AWS and Cisco;
• Proven experience with server and storage solutions, including:
- Microsoft Windows Server and Active Directory;
- Cloud Infrastructure Solutions (Microsoft Azure, AWS);
- Microsoft SQL Server environments;
- Azure and Microsoft 365 Security Frameworks;
- Virtualization: VMware vSphere, Microsoft Hyper-V;
- Storage: SAN, NAS, DAS;
- Backup & Disaster Recovery.
• General knowledge of Networking and Routing (Firewall, Routers and Switch configuration);
• Must hold one or more of the following industry certifications:
- Microsoft: MCSA, MCSE or Azure certification;
-Microsoft InTune - Endpoint Manager;
- AWS: Solutions Architect, Security Specialty;
- VMware: VCP, VCAP.
• Bachelor’s degree in Computer Science or a related ICT discipline;

Personal Attributes:
• Professionally presented;
• A positive, results-oriented and customer-focused attitude;
• Self-motivated and if required, willing to work outside the normal business working hours to meet business and client expectations;
• The ability to adapt to a changing environment that requires proactive and innovative solutions.
