***Work position: Senior accountant staff – HN office.
***Work place: 5F – VTower, 649 Kim Ma St., Ngoc Khanh Ward, Ba Dinh Dist, Ha Noi
***Working time: From Monday to Friday (8:00 – 17:00)
*** Job Description:

